\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Pol t…ôm…ôs…ôte…ôn naoa u m…ôm…ô ot…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in n…ôrat…ôn neen r…ôha nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Efesas. In t…ôm…ôte …ôm m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat. Pol t…ôm…ôtuoun nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Efesas, k…ôn m…ôtat…®g ilat min ilat o nup k…®s…®l. K…ôn in tolkeike p…®k ilat, k…ôn ilat kotolkeike p…®k in. Efesas in taon asol kit e n…®t…ôn asol u Esia, k…ôn in rum w…®r kit m…ôm…ô Pol ot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn ik…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pol tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p, ne w…ôk r…ôha nim…ôfak it…ôm in n…®p…ôt…® Iesu Kristo, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u tatuw…®n k…ôm nim…ôfak e ik…®n m…®n rafin.
\c 1
