\v 3 N…ônwiwi…ôn tuw…®n o Uhg…®n u Tata r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo r…ôhatat. E Kristo, in t…ômawte-in o narm…®tat n…ôw…®r…ôn rafin r…ôha nego e neai.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Efes 2:6 \x*
\v 4 Tol n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol…ôn …ôh neai ne n…®m…ôpt…ôn, m…ôto in t…ôm…®t…ôpun kitat m…ôm…ô kotuwa kiti…ôh kitat Kristo, k…ôn m…ôm…ô e n…®gan…ômt…®n, kitat kot…ôtuat…®p k…ôn k…ôsehm-p…ôn…ôn nol…ôn rat kit e kitat.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Jon 15:16 \x*
\v 5 M…ôto-inu Uhg…®n tolkeike p…®k kitat, uaris…®g in t…ômol nat…®mnat, m…ôto in t…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s kitat m…ôm…ô okotuwa nen…ôt…®n m…®n e Iesu Kristo. Nat …ôh tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm n…ôwian ne nat naka it…ôm in tolkeike.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Jon 1:12 \x*
