\v 8 K…ôn t…ômos-ipa n…ôw…®r…ôn …ôh it…ôm t…ôf…®g…ôm mapr…ôk…®s.
\p E nenat…®g…ôn ne n…®tun…ôn m…®n rafin r…ôhan,
\v 9 n…®kin tagien m…ôm…ô t…ômol …ôp k…ôm kitat nat anion e nalp…ôkau…ôn e r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, it…ôm in otol e Kristo.\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Rom 16:25 \x*
\v 10 K…ôn inu nalp…ôkau…ôn. E nian …ôtuat…®p r…ôhan, in ot…ôhlman nat…®mnat rafin e neai ne n…®m…ôpt…ôn okotuwa l…ôhau e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Kristo.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Kol 1:16,20 \x*
\p 
\v 11 Uhg…®n tatol nat…®mnat rafin tatuwa tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu t…ôm…ôn mihin. Aup…ôn aup…ôn ag…®n in t…ôm…®t…ôpun kitat m…ôm…ô okotuwa r…ôhan m…®n nian t…ômiuw-pa kitat kotuwa kol kiti…ôh kitat Kristo.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Rom 8:28-29 \x*
