\v 13 K…ôn it…ômat Iaihlu…ô m…®n, n…ômotuwa kiti…ôh it…ômat Kristo nian it…ômat n…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn pahrien, namnus…ôn r…ôha nosmeg…ôh…ôn. N…ômotahat…ôt…ô lan, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn Narm…®n R…ôhan k…ôm it…ômat tahmen e n…ômt…ôtin kit m…ôm…ô it…ômat r…ôhan m…®n.
\v 14 M…ôto-inu kitat k…ômotos Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn kitat kot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otos-ipa nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n k…ôm kitat it…ôm in t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô in otol mihin. Kitat okotos nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh nian Uhg…®n ot…®k…®s kitat u r…ôhan m…®n. Inu otol m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n m…ôto-inu in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt 2 Kor 1:22 \x*
