\v 17 Iat…ôfak ot…ômat k…ôm Uhg…®n it…ôm in Uhg…®n r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo r…ôhatat, k…ôn in Tata it…ôm kat…ônwiwi kat…®siai-in p…®k ag…®n. Iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô in otos-ip…®n…ô narm…®n r…ôha nenat…®g…ôn ne n…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun w…®r in t…ôhm…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Kol 1:9 \x*
