\v 19 K…ôn iat…ôfak m…®n m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôhan m…ôm…ô in iahgin p…®k ag…®n, k…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôh tatol w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat it…ôm koat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e Iesu. \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Kol 1:11 \x*K…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôh in tahmen …ôm e r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol
\v 20 it…ôm t…ômol Iesu t…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn t…ômol m…ôm…ô in t…ômuwa mat…ôp…ôl…ôh e n…®kal…® Uhg…®n mat…®p e nego e neai, ik…®n r…ôha n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne n…®siaii…ôn.\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Sam 110:1; 2 Kor 13:4; Kol 2:12 \x*
\v 21 K…ôn Iesu in il…®s e net…ôm-iasol m…®n ne nep…ôt…ôn m…®n rafin, ne n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn rafin, ne n…ôr…®g m…®n rafin, e nian u-roiu, ne e nian it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa.\x - \xo 1:21 \xt Kol 1:16; 2:10 \x*
\v 22 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nat…®mnat rafin ag…®n l…ôhau e nelk…®n, k…ôn mol in tuwa r…ôhn-kap…ô nat…®mnat rafin, k…ôn inu otasitu e nim…ôfak.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Sam 8:6 \x*
\v 23 K…ôn nim…ôfak in n…®p…ôt…® Iesu, k…ôn nalp…ôkau…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o Kristo tatuwa n…®pahrien…ôn e nim…ôfak, k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, nalp…ôkau…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o nat…®mnat rafin tatuwa pahrien e Kristo.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Rom 12:5; Efes 4:10,15; Kol 1:18 \x*
\c 2
\s1 N…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi e Kristo
\p 
\v 1 It…ômat u, aup…ôn tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô n…ômot…®m…®s m…ôto-inu n…ômot…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n, k…ôn motol nol…ôn rat m…®n.
\v 2 N…ômotan motol nol…ôn t…ôrat r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn moatol n…ôwia et…ôm t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ôrat…ôn r…ôha magoag…ôp. In …ôm …ôh narm…®n rat it…ôm tatol w…ôk roiu e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha net…ôm u koat…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:2 \xt Kol 3:7; Taet 3:3 \x*
\v 3 It…®mat m…®n emotat…®g n…ôhlan it…®mat min ilat nian kit aup…ôn. N…®kit…®mat tolkeike nol…ôn rat m…®n, k…ôn it…®mat emotol n…ôrat…ôn …ôh it…ôm k…ômotol n…®kit…®mat tagien. Nat naka it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e n…®kit…®mat ne n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhat…®mat, m…ôto it…®mat emoat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm ilat. K…ôn nian emotaiir, m…ôto nol…ôn rat t…®nat…®g r…ôk…®s e n…®kit…®mat, tahmen e net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n. K…ôn n…®ki Uhg…®n t…®tahm…ô o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhat…®mat, k…ôn in ot…ôk…ôike mol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm it…®mat.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt Kol 3:6 \x*
\v 4 M…ôto Uhg…®n, in t…ôrioah e nolkeike…ôn o kitat, k…ôn r…ôhan nas…ôkitun…ôn o kitat in iahgin p…®k.
\v 5 K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n e nian …ôh k…ômot…®m…®s e narm…®tat o r…ôhatat nol…ôn rat m…®n, m…ôto in t…ômol kitat kot…ômeg…ôh kitat Kristo m…ôto-inu in tolkeike p…®k kitat. (Ot…ôt…ôl…®g-in-tu. E n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan, in t…ômosmeg…ôh it…ômat.)\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Kol 1:21; 2:13 \x*
\v 6 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr kitat, kitat Kristo, k…ôn t…ômol m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôp…ôl…ôh kitat Kristo e nego e neai.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Kol 2:12 \x*
\v 7 Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô e nian it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa, in ot…ôg…ôtun r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm in iahgin tapr…ôk…®s ag…®n-…ôh, k…ôn kitat koat…ôplan r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn e nol…ôn w…®r r…ôhan k…ôm kitat e Kristo Iesu.
\v 8 E n…ôw…®r…ôn asol r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômawte-in k…ôm it…ômat, in t…ômosmeg…ôh it…ômat e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, k…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, s…ôn…ôm…ô it…ômat at…®p n…ômotol, m…ôto in nat kit it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ipa …ôpnap…®n …ôm k…ôm it…ômat,
\v 9 s…ôn…ôm…ô e w…ôk kit it…ôm it…ômat n…ômotol, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan ko suah kit t…ôsos-ip…ôr at…®p…ôn in ron.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Kor 1:29-31; 2 Tim 1:9 \x*
\v 10 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu in Uhg…®n it…ôm tatol w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat, k…ôn in t…ômol kitat e Kristo Iesu m…ôm…ô kitat okotol w…ôk m…®n it…ôm kot…ôw…®r. W…ôk m…®n u, Uhg…®n t…®nol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô r…ôk…®s lan m…ôm…ô kitat okotol ilat.\x - \xo 2:10 \xt Taet 2:14 \x*
\s1 Ilat k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh e Kristo
\p 
\v 11 Tol n…ôhlan, it…ômat on…ôsotaluin…ôn m…ôm…ô nian n…ômotaiir, k…ôn it…ômat s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol r…ôha Isrel. K…ôn net…ôm Isrel it…ôm k…®n…ôhg-ip…ôn r…ôk…®s ilat, ilat k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat Iaihlu…ô m…®n m…ôto-inu k…ôs…ôhg-ip…ôn…ôn it…ômat. M…ôto nat u, in nat kit it…ôm katol …ôm e n…®p…ôt…® et…ômim.
\v 12 K…ôn on…ôsotaluin…ôn m…ôm…ô e nian …ôh, it…ômat n…ômot…ôtul is…ôu o Kristo, it…ômat s…ôn…ôm…ô net…ôm Isrel …ôtuat…®p, m…ôto it…ômat Iaihlu…ô m…®n …ôm, k…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn m…®n r…ôha nasitu…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm net…ôm Isrel aup…ôn it…ôm k…ôm…ôlis ilat lan e Uhg…®n, okol t…ôsuwam…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat. N…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat e n…ôtueint…ôn u in t…ômol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô, nat kit t…®k…ô m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan, k…ôn it…ômat n…ômot…ôruru ag…®n Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Rom 9:4; Kol 1:21 \x*
\v 13 M…ôto it…ômat it…ôm aup…ôn n…ômotan is…ôu o Uhg…®n, n…ômotuwa kiti…ôh it…ômat Kristo Iesu, k…ôn roiu n…ômotuwa pahrien o Uhg…®n e n…®ta Kristo.\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Kol 1:20 \x*
\p 
\v 14 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Kristo p…®s…®n …ôm t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn, t…ôm…ôlis noanol r…ôha Isrel ne Iaihlu…ô m…®n kotuwa kiti…ôh m…ôm…ô ilat net…ôm kiti…ôh m…®n …ôm. Aup…ôn, Lou r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel in tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e noanapinat i…ôk…®s kit it…ôm t…ômatoor ilat k…ôn matol m…ôm…ô ilat koatol t…®k…®m…®r. M…ôto Kristo t…ôm…ôt…ôw…®n noanapinat …ôh.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt 1 Kor 12:13 \x*
\v 15 T…ômol n…ôhlan nian in t…ôm…®m…®s e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, k…ôn t…ômol m…ôm…ô kitat okotap…ôs n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn Lou m…®n rafin r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel m…ôm…ô okot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n. Kristo t…ômol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô in otol noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne Iaihlu…ô m…®n kotuwa kiti…ôh lan. K…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh, in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Kol 2:14 \x*
\v 16 K…ôn e n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôhan e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, Kristo t…ôm…®l…ôs ilat kotuwa kiti…ôh, k…ôn mit ilat mot…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn o Uhg…®n, k…ôn mol r…ôhalat t…®m…ôht tauke.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Sek 9:10; Kol 1:20,22 \x*
\v 17 In t…ômuwa mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…ômat u aup…ôn n…ômotat…®g is…ôu o Uhg…®n, k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…®mat u emotat…®g iu…ôhk…®r o Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:17 \xt Aes 57:19 \x*
\v 18 K…ôn roiu o nat naka it…ôm Kristo t…ômol, kitat rafin noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne Iaihlu…ô m…®n, kot…®tun nuwam…ôn o Tata Uhg…®n e Narm…®n R…ôhan kiti…ôh …ôm.
\p 
\v 19 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, s…ôn…ôm…ô it…ômat iap…®sp…®s m…®n o net…ôm ihlu…ô, m…ôto roiu it…ômat nat…®g e nego e neai it…ômat net…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, k…ôn it…ômat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 2:19 \xt Efes 3:6 \x*
\v 20 Kitat kotahmen e nim…ô kit r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm nelk…® nim…ô in Kristo Iesu, k…ôn aposol m…®n ne ien m…®n, ilat nelm…® nim…ô asol m…®n,\x - \xo 2:20 \xt 1 Kor 3:11 \x*
\v 21-22 k…ôn Kristo tat…®lp…®n it…ômat Iaihlu…ô m…®n e nim…ô …ôh tahmen e nelm…® nim…ô m…®n, k…ôn tatil…ôk…®n nelm…® nim…ô m…®n rafin m…ôm…ô ilat okotuwa nim…ô …ôtuat…®p r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn o I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ik…®n e Narm…®n R…ôhan.\x - \xo 2:21-22 \xt 1 Kor 3:16; 1 Pita 2:5 \x*
\c 3
